  "description": "VECTAETOS™ is a non-agentic onto-epistemic field framework. It describes Φ = (Σ, R) as a formal topology of invariant, non-hierarchical singularities and antisymmetric relational tensions. The repository includes canonical ontology materials, implementation-boundary documents, projection / trace governance, software/tooling guards, and a layered custom license stack. VECTAETOS™ is not an autonomous agent, decision system, optimizer, recommendation engine, deployment validator, safety guarantee, or truth authority.",
